<section xml:id="C4.S35">
<title>Identities</title>          
<subsection xml:id="C4.S35.SS1">
<title>Addition Formulas</title>          
<para xml:id="C4.S35.SS1.p1">

<sentence sentence-num-in-para="1" sentence-num-in-section="1" xml:id="C4.S35.SS1.p1.s1">
 <Math equation-number="4.35.1" mode="display" xml:id="C4.S35.E1">\sinh\left(u\pm v\right)=\sinh u\cosh v\pm\cosh u\sinh v,</Math> , <Math equation-number="4.35.2" mode="display" xml:id="C4.S35.E2">\cosh\left(u\pm v\right)=\cosh u\cosh v\pm\sinh u\sinh v,</Math> , <Math equation-number="4.35.3" mode="display" xml:id="C4.S35.E3">\tanh\left(u\pm v\right)=\frac{\tanh u\pm\tanh v}{1\pm\tanh u\tanh v},</Math> , <Math equation-number="4.35.4" mode="display" xml:id="C4.S35.E4">\coth\left(u\pm v\right)=\frac{\pm\coth u\coth v+1}{\coth u\pm\coth v}</Math>.
</sentence>

<sentence sentence-num-in-para="2" sentence-num-in-section="2" xml:id="C4.S35.SS1.p1.s2">
<Math equation-number="4.35.5" mode="display" xml:id="C4.S35.E5">\sinh u+\sinh v=2\sinh\left(\frac{u+v}{2}\right)\cosh\left(\frac{u-v}{2}\right),</Math> , <Math equation-number="4.35.6" mode="display" xml:id="C4.S35.E6">\sinh u-\sinh v=2\cosh\left(\frac{u+v}{2}\right)\sinh\left(\frac{u-v}{2}\right),</Math> , <Math equation-number="4.35.7" mode="display" xml:id="C4.S35.E7">\cosh u+\cosh v=2\cosh\left(\frac{u+v}{2}\right)\cosh\left(\frac{u-v}{2}\right),</Math> , <Math equation-number="4.35.8" mode="display" xml:id="C4.S35.E8">\cosh u-\cosh v=2\sinh\left(\frac{u+v}{2}\right)\sinh\left(\frac{u-v}{2}\right),</Math> , <Math equation-number="4.35.9" mode="display" xml:id="C4.S35.E9">\tanh u\pm\tanh v=\frac{\sinh\left(u\pm v\right)}{\cosh u\cosh v},</Math> , <Math equation-number="4.35.10" mode="display" xml:id="C4.S35.E10">\coth u\pm\coth v=\frac{\sinh\left(v\pm u\right)}{\sinh u\sinh v}</Math>.
</sentence>

</para>
 
</subsection>
 
<subsection xml:id="C4.S35.SS2">
<title>Squares and Products</title>          
<para xml:id="C4.S35.SS2.p1">

<sentence sentence-num-in-para="1" sentence-num-in-section="3" xml:id="C4.S35.SS2.p1.s1">
 <Math equation-number="4.35.11" mode="display" xml:id="C4.S35.E11">{\cosh^{2}}z-{\sinh^{2}}z=1,</Math> <Math equation-number="4.35.12" mode="display" xml:id="C4.S35.E12">{\operatorname{sech}^{2}}z=1-{\tanh^{2}}z,</Math> <Math equation-number="4.35.13" mode="display" xml:id="C4.S35.E13">{\operatorname{csch}^{2}}z={\coth^{2}}z-1</Math>.
</sentence>

<sentence sentence-num-in-para="2" sentence-num-in-section="4" xml:id="C4.S35.SS2.p1.s2">
<Math equation-number="4.35.14" mode="display" xml:id="C4.S35.E14">2\sinh u\sinh v=\cosh\left(u+v\right)-\cosh\left(u-v\right),</Math> , <Math equation-number="4.35.15" mode="display" xml:id="C4.S35.E15">2\cosh u\cosh v=\cosh\left(u+v\right)+\cosh\left(u-v\right),</Math> , <Math equation-number="4.35.16" mode="display" xml:id="C4.S35.E16">2\sinh u\cosh v=\sinh\left(u+v\right)+\sinh\left(u-v\right)</Math>.
</sentence>

<sentence sentence-num-in-para="3" sentence-num-in-section="5" xml:id="C4.S35.SS2.p1.s3">
<Math equation-number="4.35.17" mode="display" xml:id="C4.S35.E17">{\sinh^{2}}u-{\sinh^{2}}v=\sinh\left(u+v\right)\sinh\left(u-v\right),</Math> , <Math equation-number="4.35.18" mode="display" xml:id="C4.S35.E18">{\cosh^{2}}u-{\cosh^{2}}v=\sinh\left(u+v\right)\sinh\left(u-v\right),</Math> , <Math equation-number="4.35.19" mode="display" xml:id="C4.S35.E19">{\sinh^{2}}u+{\cosh^{2}}v=\cosh\left(u+v\right)\cosh\left(u-v\right)</Math>.
</sentence>

</para>
 
</subsection>
 
<subsection xml:id="C4.S35.SS3">
<title>Multiples of the Argument</title>          
<para xml:id="C4.S35.SS3.p1">

<sentence sentence-num-in-para="1" sentence-num-in-section="6" xml:id="C4.S35.SS3.p1.s1">
 <Math equation-number="4.35.20" mode="display" xml:id="C4.S35.E20">\sinh\frac{z}{2}=\left(\frac{\cosh z-1}{2}\right)^{1/2},</Math> <Math equation-number="4.35.21" mode="display" xml:id="C4.S35.E21">\cosh\frac{z}{2}=\left(\frac{\cosh z+1}{2}\right)^{1/2},</Math> <Math equation-number="4.35.22" mode="display" xml:id="C4.S35.E22">\tanh\frac{z}{2}=\left(\frac{\cosh z-1}{\cosh z+1}\right)^{1/2}=\frac{\cosh z- 1}{\sinh z}=\frac{\sinh z}{\cosh z+1}</Math>.
</sentence>

<sentence sentence-num-in-para="2" sentence-num-in-section="7" xml:id="C4.S35.SS3.p1.s2">
The square roots assume their principal value on the positive real axis, and are determined by continuity elsewhere.
</sentence>

<sentence sentence-num-in-para="3" sentence-num-in-section="8" xml:id="C4.S35.SS3.p1.s3">
<Math equation-number="4.35.23" mode="display" xml:id="C4.S35.E23">\sinh\left(-z\right)=-\sinh z,</Math> , <Math equation-number="4.35.24" mode="display" xml:id="C4.S35.E24">\cosh\left(-z\right)=\cosh z,</Math> , <Math equation-number="4.35.25" mode="display" xml:id="C4.S35.E25">\tanh\left(-z\right)=-\tanh z</Math>.
</sentence>

<sentence sentence-num-in-para="4" sentence-num-in-section="9" xml:id="C4.S35.SS3.p1.s4">
<Math equation-number="4.35.26" mode="display" xml:id="C4.S35.E26">\sinh\left(2z\right)=2\sinh z\cosh z=\frac{2\tanh z}{1-{\tanh^{2}}z},</Math> <Math equation-number="4.35.27" mode="display" xml:id="C4.S35.E27">\cosh\left(2z\right)=2{\cosh^{2}}z-1=2{\sinh^{2}}z+1\\ ={\cosh^{2}}z+{\sinh^{2}}z,</Math> <Math equation-number="4.35.28" mode="display" xml:id="C4.S35.E28">\tanh\left(2z\right)=\frac{2\tanh z}{1+{\tanh^{2}}z},</Math> <Math equation-number="4.35.29" mode="display" xml:id="C4.S35.E29">\sinh\left(3z\right)=3\sinh z+4{\sinh^{3}}z,</Math> <Math equation-number="4.35.30" mode="display" xml:id="C4.S35.E30">\cosh\left(3z\right)=-3\cosh z+4{\cosh^{3}}z,</Math> <Math equation-number="4.35.31" mode="display" xml:id="C4.S35.E31">\sinh\left(4z\right)=4{\sinh^{3}}z\cosh z+4{\cosh^{3}}z\sinh z,</Math> , <Math equation-number="4.35.32" mode="display" xml:id="C4.S35.E32">\cosh\left(4z\right)={\cosh^{4}}z+6{\sinh^{2}}z{\cosh^{2}}z+{\sinh^{4}}z</Math>.
</sentence>

<sentence sentence-num-in-para="5" sentence-num-in-section="10" xml:id="C4.S35.SS3.p1.s5">
<Math equation-number="4.35.33" mode="display" xml:id="C4.S35.E33">\cosh\left(nz\right)\pm\sinh\left(nz\right)=(\cosh z\pm\sinh z)^{n}, if n\in\mathbb{Z}</Math>.
</sentence>

</para>
 
</subsection>
 
<subsection xml:id="C4.S35.SS4">
<title>Real and Imaginary Parts; Moduli</title>           
<para xml:id="C4.S35.SS4.p1">

<sentence sentence-num-in-para="1" sentence-num-in-section="11" xml:id="C4.S35.SS4.p1.s1">
With <Math mode="inline" xml:id="C4.S35.SS4.p1.m1">z=x+iy</Math> <Math equation-number="4.35.34" mode="display" xml:id="C4.S35.E34">\sinh z=\sinh x\cos y+i\cosh x\sin y,</Math> , <Math equation-number="4.35.35" mode="display" xml:id="C4.S35.E35">\cosh z=\cosh x\cos y+i\sinh x\sin y,</Math> , <Math equation-number="4.35.36" mode="display" xml:id="C4.S35.E36">\tanh z=\frac{\sinh\left(2x\right)+i\sin\left(2y\right)}{\cosh\left(2x\right)+ \cos\left(2y\right)},</Math> , <Math equation-number="4.35.37" mode="display" xml:id="C4.S35.E37">\coth z=\frac{\sinh\left(2x\right)-i\sin\left(2y\right)}{\cosh\left(2x\right)- \cos\left(2y\right)}</Math>.
</sentence>

<sentence sentence-num-in-para="2" sentence-num-in-section="12" xml:id="C4.S35.SS4.p1.s2">
<Math equation-number="4.35.38" mode="display" xml:id="C4.S35.E38">|\sinh z|=({\sinh^{2}}x+{\sin^{2}}y)^{1/2}=\left(\tfrac{1}{2}(\cosh\left(2x \right)-\cos\left(2y\right))\right)^{1/2},</Math> <Math equation-number="4.35.39" mode="display" xml:id="C4.S35.E39">|\cosh z|=({\sinh^{2}}x+{\cos^{2}}y)^{1/2}=\left(\tfrac{1}{2}(\cosh\left(2x \right)+\cos\left(2y\right))\right)^{1/2},</Math> <Math equation-number="4.35.40" mode="display" xml:id="C4.S35.E40">|\tanh z|=\left(\frac{\cosh\left(2x\right)-\cos\left(2y\right)}{\cosh\left(2x \right)+\cos\left(2y\right)}\right)^{1/2}</Math>.
</sentence>

</para>
 
</subsection>
 
</section>
